    Open Grid Forum NSI Connection Services Protocol v2.0

    Description: This is a draft version of the types schema for the reference web services implementation of the OGF NSI Connection Services Protocol v2.0. This can be considered the transport independent protocol representation.  Comments and questions can be directed to the mailing list group mailing list (nsi-wg@ogf.org).
